<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>New Challenge Assigned</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333333;
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #ffffff;
      background-color: #007BFF;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999999;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <p>Hi {{studentName}},</p>

    <p>Exciting news! You have been assigned a new challenge called <strong>“{{challengeName}}”</strong> by
      <strong>{{assignedBy}}</strong> on TruPreneurs.AI 🎉</p>

    <p>Log in now to explore the challenge and share your ideas 💡</p>

    {{!-- <a href="{{ChallengeLink}}" class="button">View Challenge</a> --}}

    <p class="footer">
      Best Regards,<br>
      TruPreneurs.AI
    </p>
  </div>
</body>

</html>